    "description": "Create a modern website for a wellness-focused gym called “Balance Movement”.\n\nConcept:\nCombination of yoga, pilates, functional training, and mindfulness.\n\nAudience:\nPeople aged 25–45 seeking balanced health and stress relief.\n\nTone:\nCalm, positive, supportive.\n\nMain colors:\n- Soft teal\n- Light sand/beige\n- White backgrounds\n- Muted coral accents\n\nGoals:\nEncourage trial class bookings.\n\nStructure:\n- Hero with calming message\n- Wellness philosophy\n- Class offerings\n- Instructor highlights\n- Testimonials\n- Intro offer section\n- Booking CTA\n\nDesign guidance:\n- Light, airy layout\n- Lots of whitespace\n- Natural lifestyle imagery\n- Soft section transitions\n- Rounded visual elements\n\nCopy guidance:\n- Encouraging and human tone\n- Focus on well-being, not aesthetics\n- Avoid extreme fitness language\n\nMake it feel like a wellness sanctuary, not a hardcore gym.\nKeep it realistic and inviting.",
